{"tid":1053364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委國停電斷網 雙胞政權互轟","createTime":"2019-03-09T04:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T04:31:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb8d8ec6765ee50b76bb3fc3488c441ccabe1e42","tid":1053364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190309/20629446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F20629446&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=ea6cfeab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190309%2F20629446&h=4f2f6565\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190309/20629446</a><br />\n<br />\n委國停電斷網 雙胞政權互轟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190309/large/09wx04p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190309%2Flarge%2F09wx04p.jpg&h=586be158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n停電沒路燈下，卡拉卡斯市民摸黑在車頭燈光中過馬路。 美聯社<br />\n<br />\n經濟陷困境的委內瑞拉前日傍晚大停電，互聯網絡亦中斷，政府昨宣佈全國停工停課，又不點名指摘是反對派破壞發電機所致，但反對派和民眾都說最要負責的是總統馬杜羅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民眾爆粗「問候」馬杜羅<br />\n<br />\n停電在下午4時50分下班時間發生，除了少數自設發電機的大廈外，首都卡拉卡斯全城一片漆黑，電話、互聯網和地鐵全部中斷，大路中滿是摸黑走路回家的人潮，全國23省至少15個亦停電。久久未恢復供電，民眾漸不耐煩，在家中開窗敲鍋敲盤抗議，甚至爆粗「問候」馬杜羅。<br />\n<br />\n國家電力公司CORPOELEC代表推文說「他們破壞了中央發電機」，會盡快讓電力復原，但未說明「他們」是誰。總統馬杜羅就推文說這是一場美國發動的「電力戰爭」。自封臨時總統的瓜伊多推文反擊：「到委內瑞拉結束專權自會回復光明。」委國倚靠的中央水力發電廠位於玻利維亞東部，是拉丁美洲最大規模電力基建之一。貪腐加上國庫緊絀，令委內瑞拉欠經費維護發電設施，經常停電，但政府在沒有證據的情況下，屢次不點名指摘是反對派搞鬼。<br />\n<br />\n法新社  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n對特金會破局表不滿  朝重啟導彈發射場<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n英行使外交保護權促伊朗放人"},{"pid":"57246039d7c715f86f95b43b4b8b4b81bb8deae2","tid":1053364,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4e635fc0371cd38b7316a645c7ffce488fdb20","tid":1053364,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"場自由杯搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d2bf3d54d94e5d3aa9e29ce0dd4833e1fc687a","tid":1053364,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:17:03.000Z","msg":"快撚啲收個仆街政權皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec91d5c3056faefe2031d931997c590d86b8aa69","tid":1053364,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"連電力都俾美國控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78007705bc28afdea9696e6b030aba6c23e0cf6a","tid":1053364,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:21:16.000Z","msg":"網都上唔到，唔使捉五美仙黨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163844f40b5e25ff6335904a843454ab52d33c1e","tid":1053364,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T04:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>委國倚靠的中央水力發電廠位於玻利維亞東部，是拉丁美洲最大規模電力基建之一。貪腐加上國庫緊絀，令委內瑞拉欠經費維護發電設施，經常停電，但政府在沒有證據的情況下，屢次不點名指摘是反對派搞鬼。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀到呢度都覺得奇怪，點解委內瑞拉要用玻利維亞嘅發電廠<br />\n<br />\n走去睇CNN，人哋咁樣寫：<br />\nHe alleged, without offering evidence, that the attack took place at Venezuela's main hydroelectric power station in Guri in the southern state of Bolivar, which provides about 70% of the country's energy.<br />\n<br />\n原來講緊委內瑞拉嘅玻利華州，呢個州東部有個叫Guri嘅水壩愛嚟發電，屌你華文傳媒真係戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}